1. Create a branch for the component you’re working on.
2. Clone the branch from our remote repo onto your computer.
Open Git Bash in the appropriate folder.
Use command: git clone --single-branch --branch <branch_name> <repo_url>
3. Add your changes to the staging area
git add .
4. Commit the changes from the staging area
git commit -m “Comment here”
5. Push the changes to the branch you created earlier
git push origin <branch_name>
